item.description: <title>Warm Winter in Stonebridge</title>This kitchen uses warm and cool tones bring a unique style to the space, featuring Winter White cabinets with a Walnut Glaze in Stonebridge style and Granite certified by Kitchen Magic countertops in Juparana Crema Bordeaux with a Roundover edge.
